author: Cleo Abram
description:
What’s the longest anyone has ever held their breath? 

Do not try this at home. 

The official record for holding your breath and no air moving is…

But with pure oxygen? Subscribe if you think it’s longer than 20 minutes! 

This is Huge If True, our optimistic show about science and technology.

#shorts #science #oxygen #breathing #recordbreaking #technology
title: What If You Just Kept Holding Your Breath?
